OL,3,CPolice issue fresh appeal to find
OL,4,Cmissing man on one year anniversary
OL,6,FDetectives have issued a fresh appeal
OL,7,Ffor help to find a missing man from
OL,8,FOxford, on the one year anniversary of
OL,9,Fhis disappearance.
OL,11,FStephen, 54, has not been heard from
OL,12,Fsince 30 March 2025.
OL,14,FHe was reported missing almost a month
OL,15,Flater on Sunday 20 April.
OL,17,FPolice say he stopped at the East
OL,18,FIsley Shell at approximately 8.15pm on
OL,19,F31 March, where he bought a five-litre
OL,20,Ffuel can.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
