PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774966279
OL,3,CPolice issue fresh appeal to find
OL,4,Cmissing man on one year anniversary
OL,6,FHe then travelled by car, a blue Mazda
OL,7,F3, which was then abandoned by a field
OL,8,Fon the Ridgeway near Southfields,
OL,9,FAldworth in West Berkshire.
OL,11,FStephen's car and the area were
OL,12,Fsearched, but officers say a fuel can
OL,13,Fwasn't found.
OL,15,FStephen is 5ft 11ins tall, of slim
OL,16,Fbuild, and may be wearing blue jeans,
OL,17,Fan open necked top, striped cardigan,
OL,18,Fwalking boots and glasses. He is known
OL,19,Fto carry a backpack with him.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
