CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774966279
OL,3,CPolice issue fresh appeal to find
OL,4,Cmissing man on one year anniversary
OL,6,FHe also has links to Littlehampton in
OL,7,FWest Sussex.
OL,9,FLead investigating officer, Detective
OL,10,FInspector Elizabeth Batchelor, said:
OL,11,F"Ever since Stephen was reported
OL,12,Fmissing in April last year, we have
OL,13,Fbeen growing increasingly concerned
OL,14,Ffor his welfare.
OL,16,F"Our officers have searched the
OL,17,FRidgeway, where his car was abandoned
OL,18,Fwith support from Berkshire Lowland
OL,19,FSearch and Rescue and have been
OL,20,Fcontinuing to make enquiries in an
OL,21,Feffort to trace him.
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
