FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774966279
OL,3,CPolice issue fresh appeal to find
OL,4,Cmissing man on one year anniversary
OL,6,F"We have been working hard to find
OL,7,FStephen since he was reported missing
OL,8,Fand we are still appealing for the
OL,9,Fpublic's help to locate him so if you
OL,10,Fsee Stephen, please call 999, quoting
OL,11,Freference number 43250192691.
OL,13,F"We are also appealing to anyone who
OL,14,Fmay have picked up a green five-litre
OL,15,Ffuel can, like the one pictured, on or
OL,16,Faround the time that he went missing,
OL,17,Fas we believe that this person(s) may
OL,18,Fhave information that could assist our
OL,19,Fsearch. The can may have been filled
OL,20,Fwith unleaded petrol.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774966279
OL,3,CPolice issue fresh appeal to find
OL,4,Cmissing man on one year anniversary
OL,6,F"We are also asking anyone who may
OL,7,Fhave seen or spoken to Stephen on
OL,8,FThursday 27 March 2025 to please get
OL,9,Fin touch.
OL,11,F"Anyone with information on Stephen's
OL,12,Fwhereabouts, no matter how
OL,13,Finsignificant or small it may seem,
OL,14,Fplease make a report via our website.
OL,16,F"Stephen, if you see this appeal,
OL,17,Fplease know that you are not in any
OL,18,Ftrouble, but we are concerned for you.
OL,19,FSo, please contact us and let us know
OL,20,Fwhere you are."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU|D@OO]
